sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Human
    participant GN as /go-nogo
    participant CL as /changelog
    participant Cfg as Company Config
    participant PI as ~/.claude/pi/[current-pi]/plan.md
    participant FS as docs/releases/

    H->>GN: /go-nogo

    GN->>Cfg: Read freeze_periods, compliance_tier, external_approval, release_cadence
    GN->>PI: Identify release (PI-N-RN) + deployment date
    GN->>FS: Read kanban per active project (completed vs incomplete)
    GN->>FS: Read sprint records for this release cycle
    GN->>FS: Read known-issues.md (Active issues)

    note over GN: Freeze period check
    alt Deployment date inside no-deploy freeze
        GN->>H: 🚫 FREEZE — recommends NO-GO
    else Deployment date inside warn-only freeze
        GN->>H: ⚠️ Freeze advisory — human decides
    else Approaching freeze window
        GN->>H: ⚠️ Freeze in N days — verify timeline
    end

    note over GN: Security assessment check
    alt Security assessment overdue
        GN->>H: ⚠️ Security assessment overdue (regulated → required)
    end

    GN->>FS: Save docs/releases/PI-N-RN-gono.md (brief)
    GN->>H: Present Go/No Go brief. Type GO or NO-GO

    alt GO
        alt External approval configured
            GN->>H: Has [approval-name] been obtained? (reference / confirmed)
            H->>GN: Confirmation captured
        end
        H->>GN: GO
        GN->>PI: Update release status → Approved
        GN->>FS: Record decision in brief
        GN->>H: Deployment date confirmed — suggest /changelog + /deploy

        H->>CL: /changelog
        CL->>FS: Read kanban + DEVLOG + git log
        CL->>FS: Generate CHANGELOG.md + user-facing release summary
    else NO-GO
        H->>GN: NO-GO
        GN->>H: Which features carry forward to next release?
        H->>GN: Feature list
        GN->>PI: Defer features to next release
        GN->>FS: Update kanban.md (carry-forward flags)
        GN->>FS: Note in DEVLOG — release deferred
        GN->>H: Suggest /diagnose or /sprint-replan
    end
